'Docket' may refer to:

*Docket (court), the official schedule of proceedings in lawsuits pending in a
court of law. *Agenda (meeting) or docket, a list of meeting activities in the
order in which they are to be taken up *Receipt or tax invoice, a proof of
payment for items purchased *, e.g. Air Waybill, Bill of Lading or CMR
